"Similarly, @kbd{C-x 5 b} (@code{switch-to-buffer-other-frame})  prompts for "
"a buffer name, displays that buffer in another frame, and selects that "
"frame.  If the buffer is already being shown in a window on another frame, "
"Emacs selects that window and frame instead of creating a new frame."
